text: Vasile Coșelev (; born 12 February 1972 in Chișinău) is a former Moldovan football player. Between 1992–1999 Vasile Coșelev has played 23 matches for Moldova national football team.NATIONAL TEAM appearances of Vasile Coșelev ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1972 births Category:Sportspeople from Chișinău Category:Living people Category:FC Zimbru Chișinău players Category:Soviet footballers Category:FC Zaria Bălți players Category:SKA Odessa players Category:Moldovan footballers Category:Moldova international footballers Category:CS Tiligul-Tiras Tiraspol players Category:FC Tiraspol players Category:FC Krylia Sovetov Samara players Category:Moldovan expatriate footballers Category:Russian Premier League players Category:FC Elista players Category:FC Rapid Ghidighici players Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:FC Dynamo Vologda players Category:FC Sodovik Sterlitamak players
